---

<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
  <!-- Encabezado de introducción -->
  <div class="text-center mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-dm-serif font-normal text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6 text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl">
      Soluciones integrales para tu empresa: asesoría fiscal, laboral y contable con enfoque estratégico.
    </h2>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-base">
      <p>
        Te ayudamos a optimizar tu negocio desde todos los ángulos: fiscalidad, gestión laboral, contabilidad y más.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base italic">
        Una visión 360º, adaptada a tus necesidades específicas.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Layout profesional con diseño moderno -->
  <div class="space-y-8 mb-12">
    
    <!-- Asesoría Fiscal -->
    <div class="group relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-50 via-amber-50 to-orange-50 dark:from-yellow-900/20 dark:via-amber-900/20 dark:to-orange-900/20 rounded-2xl border border-yellow-200 dark:border-yellow-700 hover:border-yellow-300 dark:hover:border-yellow-600 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1">
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-bl from-yellow-200/20 to-transparent rounded-full transform translate-x-16 -translate-y-16"></div>
      
      <div class="relative p-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center">
          <!-- Icono y título -->
          <div class="lg:col-span-3">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-4 lg:mb-0">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-yellow-700 dark:text-yellow-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-dm-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-xl mb-1">
                  Asesoría Fiscal
                </h3>
                <p class="text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400 text-sm font-medium">
                  Optimización inteligente
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Contenido principal -->
          <div class="lg:col-span-6">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-base mb-4">
              Optimiza tu carga fiscal con estrategias claras y eficientes. No recurrimos a atajos: te ayudamos a planificar de forma inteligente para pagar solo lo necesario.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span>Declaraciones fiscales</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span>Planificación estratégica</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span>Representación ante Hacienda</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span>Asesoría personalizada</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- CTA -->
          <div class="lg:col-span-3 text-center lg:text-right">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-medium text-sm mb-3">
              ¿Listo para optimizar tu fiscalidad?
            </p>
            <a
              href="/haion_landing/fiscal"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-yellow-400 hover:bg-yellow-500 text-gray-900 font-semibold rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
            >
              Conoce más
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Asesoría Laboral -->
    <div class="group relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-50 via-yellow-50 to-orange-50 dark:from-amber-900/20 dark:via-yellow-900/20 dark:to-orange-900/20 rounded-2xl border border-yellow-200 dark:border-yellow-700 hover:border-yellow-300 dark:hover:border-yellow-600 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-200/20 to-transparent rounded-full transform -translate-x-16 -translate-y-16"></div>
      
      <div class="relative p-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center">
          <!-- Icono y título -->
          <div class="lg:col-span-3">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-4 lg:mb-0">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-amber-200 dark:bg-amber-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-dm-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-xl mb-1">
                  Asesoría Laboral
                </h3>
                <p class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 text-sm font-medium">
                  Gestión de equipos
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Contenido principal -->
          <div class="lg:col-span-6">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-base mb-4">
              Cuidamos a tus equipos y aseguramos el cumplimiento normativo. Nos encargamos de las complejidades laborales para que puedas enfocarte en tu negocio.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-amber-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span>Gestión de nóminas</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-amber-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span>Contrataciones y despidos</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-amber-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span>Inspecciones laborales</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-amber-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span>Convenios colectivos</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- CTA -->
          <div class="lg:col-span-3 text-center lg:text-right">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-medium text-sm mb-3">
              ¿Todo bajo control laboral?
            </p>
            <a
              href="/haion_landing/laboral"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-amber-400 hover:bg-amber-500 text-gray-900 font-semibold rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
            >
              Conoce más
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Asesoría Contable -->
    <div class="group relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-50 via-amber-50 to-yellow-50 dark:from-orange-900/20 dark:via-amber-900/20 dark:to-yellow-900/20 rounded-2xl border border-yellow-200 dark:border-yellow-700 hover:border-yellow-300 dark:hover:border-yellow-600 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1">
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-tl from-orange-200/20 to-transparent rounded-full transform translate-x-16 translate-y-16"></div>
      
      <div class="relative p-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center">
          <!-- Icono y título -->
          <div class="lg:col-span-3">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-4 lg:mb-0">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-orange-200 dark:bg-orange-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-700 dark:text-orange-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-dm-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-xl mb-1">
                  Asesoría Contable
                </h3>
                <p class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 text-sm font-medium">
                  Decisiones estratégicas
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Contenido principal -->
          <div class="lg:col-span-6">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-base mb-4">
              Tus números no son solo cifras: son decisiones estratégicas. Te ayudamos a entender cada dato para que puedas tomar las mejores decisiones financieras.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-orange-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span>Contabilidad rigurosa</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-orange-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span>Balances y cuentas anuales</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-orange-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span>Informes personalizados</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-orange-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span>Gestión fiscal integrada</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- CTA -->
          <div class="lg:col-span-3 text-center lg:text-right">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-medium text-sm mb-3">
              ¿Control total financiero?
            </p>
            <a
              href="/haion_landing/contable"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-orange-400 hover:bg-orange-500 text-gray-900 font-semibold rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
            >
              Conoce más
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>